title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 96: Featuring Keith Yandle & Kevin Hayes
description:
On this week's episode, the guys are recording live from the house of Florida Panthers defenseman Keith Yandle. The boys are also joined by New York Rangers forward Kevin Hayes for the entire episode. On the agenda for the episode is John Tavares and the meeting he held in LA with potential teams for next season, the Hall of Fame inductees, more man rockets, Biz joined a gym & much more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
